member.name: F:Microsoft.Maps.Plugins.Cardinality.Multiple
member.summary: A multiple import allows multiple instances of a contract.A multiple export offers multiple instances of a contract.

member.name: F:Microsoft.Maps.Plugins.Cardinality.Single
member.summary: A single import requires that the contract instance be present exactly once across all plug-ins on the Bing Maps site.A single export indicates that the contract instance is offered exactly once by this plugin.
